        <b>About Hotel :</b><br />
        <img border="0" height="1" hspace="0" src="http://www.kerala-tourism.net/gifs1/bdline.gif"
            vspace="2" width="243" /><br />
        Hotel Leela Kovalam Beach Resort is the refined specimen of a magnificent blend
        of simplicity and modernity, that has made it one of the best hotels in terms of
        service and care. Perched at a distance of 15 kms from Trivendrum, the Leela Kempinski
        Kovalam Beach Resort, Kerala is built on a rock-face and is cradled between two
        wide sweeping beaches and has a panoramic view of the famous Kovalam coastline.Being
        rigged between two wide beaches, the hotel boasts of 194 lavishly decorated rooms
        and suites. Sprawling over 44 acres of landscaped area, Leela Beach Resort is an
        oasis of luxury. Its location is an added advantage, providing an absorbing and
        breathtaking vista of Kovalam coastline. This 5 star deluxe resort, with an array
        of superlative restaurants and lounges, also specializes in traditional Ayurveda
        treatment.All Beach-View guestrooms have private sundecks. Two stunning infinity
        pools overlook the Arabian Sea. Guests at the hotel can enjoy a seaside stroll and
        can have the feel of the ocean any time they want. The Sea-View Wing houses The
        Club at The Leela and is perched on a cliff overlooking the sea.<br />
