    <div align="justify" class="txt">
        <b>Accommodation at Hotel Leela Kovalam Beach Resort :</b><br />
        <img border="0" height="1" hspace="0" src="http://www.kerala-tourism.net/gifs1/bdline.gif"
            vspace="2" width="243" /><br />
        The Leela Kovalam Beach Resort is embellished with 194 exquisitely designed rooms
        and suites. These luxurious accommodations are divided into different categories
        and groups to cater varied taste, style and comfort of the customers. There are
        88 rooms in Beach-view Wing, 42 rooms in Pavilion Wing and 60 rooms in Sea-view
        Club Wing. All the rooms are adorned with superb blend of comfort and luxury. Every
        room accommodation is furnished with television with satellite channels, direct
        dialing telephone, in-room digital safe, mini bar, tea/coffee making facility and
        en-suite bath with hairdryer.
        <br />
        <br />
        Rooms also have a beautiful balcony to enjoy a cup of coffee at the dawn or for
        having a romantic chat in the evening. Also multi-cuisine restaurants will leave
        you asking for more.
        <br />
        <br />
        <br />
        <b>Dining :</b><br />
        <img border="0" height="1" hspace="0" src="http://www.kerala-tourism.net/gifs1/bdline.gif"
            vspace="2" width="243" /><br />
        The Leela Kovalam Beach Kerala hotel has a lot to offer when it comes to dining
        in luxurious style. The Café, multi-cuisine restaurant that serves buffet style
        and attracts food lovers with a wood fired pizza oven; crispy snacks and beverages
        at Pool Lounge; a Bar with an unparallel view of the beach; and the Beach Restaurant
        that not only makes your tongues twirl but also your feet at the dance floor amidst
        live music.<br />
        <br />
        <br />
        <b>Conference and Banquet Facilities :</b><br />
        <img border="0" height="1" hspace="0" src="http://www.kerala-tourism.net/gifs1/bdline.gif"
            vspace="2" width="243" /><br />
        The Leela Kovalam Beach Kerala has state of the art and efficient Co invention Center
        and Meeting Rooms that cater to all your business needs and requirements.<br />
        <br />
        <br />
        <b>Recreation and Spa Facilities :</b><br />
        <img border="0" height="1" hspace="0" src="http://www.kerala-tourism.net/gifs1/bdline.gif"
            vspace="2" width="243" /><br />
        In between looming deadlines and tight timelines, we forget to take the time to
        just live a little. That is why an integral part of living the Leela life is taking
        time off to relax, rejuvenate and rediscover oneself.<br />
        <br />
        <b>Spa :</b> Sipping sundowners at the beach or returning after a 12 hour work-day,
        you'll find the perfect range of treatments and therapies at every Leela Hotel.<br />
        So whether you're flying high at one of our business hotels or escaping to one of
        our luxury resorts, you'll find that each Leela Hotel has a spa that perfect for
        both the person and the place.<br />
        <br />
        <b>Watersports :</b> India has around 7000 kilometres of coastline and some of the
        best beaches in the world. Add to that the sunny, tropical climate and you have
        the perfect recipe for some exhilarating water sports. If it’s a romantic boat-ride
        you fancy or an afternoon of splashing around with the whole family, you can be
        sure to find it at the Leela Hotels, Palaces and Resorts. Or in the seas off our
        properties, to be more precise.<br />
        <br />
        <b>Golf :</b> If you prefer the company of a caddy to that of a cocktail, you’re
        staying at the right chain of business hotels and luxury resorts. For at the Leela
        Hotels, Palaces and Resorts, we take golf as seriously as you do. The Leela Goa
        has its own 12 hole, par 3 course. And access to some of the country’s best courses
        is easily arranged at other properties. Do remember to check up when you check in.
